 <title>Quick Start Step 2: <keyword keyref="quickStartHPcloudStep2"/></title>
 <shortdesc>During this step you will download and install the tools necessary for creating a
    cluster and pushing applications to your sandbox environment. The download links and
    instructions will open in separate pages.</shortdesc>
 <prolog>
  <metadata>
   <othermeta name="author" content="Michael Khmelnitsky"/>
  </metadata>
 </prolog>
 <conbody>
